329
00:17:08,520 --> 00:17:09,700
Mentor, I'm…

330
00:17:14,310 --> 00:17:15,420
My bad. My bad.

331
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:16,570
Oh my God.

332
00:17:16,590 --> 00:17:16,980
I

333
