466
00:23:03,600 --> 00:23:04,340
Mentor.

467
00:23:05,080 --> 00:23:05,620
Mentor.

468
00:23:05,760 --> 00:23:06,300
Mr. Guo, you're here.

469
00:23:07,000 --> 00:23:07,540
