559
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:24,220
Alright.

560
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:27,020
He's already like this.

561
00:27:27,240 --> 00:27:28,380
Don't let it weigh on you.

562
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:31,140
We were

563
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:32,700
just talking

564
00:27:32,840 --> 00:27:34,460
