566
00:27:37,480 --> 00:27:39,220
We had a great chat.

567
00:27:45,440 --> 00:27:46,460
Sometimes,

568
00:27:47,600 --> 00:27:49,860
I actually envy him.

569
00:27:50,960 --> 00:27:52,700
All the messy things in life…

570
00:27:53,040 --> 00:27:54,980
I wish I could forget them, but I can't.

571
00:28:02,520 --> 00:28:03,340
Chen.

572
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:08,420
Tell me about you and Fei.

573
00:28:11,240 --> 00:28:12,380
You're…

574
00:28:13,080 --> 00:28:14,660
Cong's wife?

575
00:28:14,840 --> 00:28:16,700
No, no.

576
00:28:16,760 --> 00:28:17,100
I…

577
00:28:17,360 --> 00:28:19,340
I'm his trainee.

578
00:28:21,120 --> 00:28:22,460
Look at me, I forgot.

579
00:28:22,480 --> 00:28:23,300
Right, right.

580
00:28:23,320 --> 00:28:23,940
Trainee.

581
00:28:23,960 --> 00:28:25,860
You just said that.

582
00:28:26,720 --> 00:28:27,900
Guo Cong's girlfriend.

583
00:28:27,920 --> 00:28:28,740
Right, right.

584
00:28:29,040 --> 00:28:30,540
That's nice. Really nice.

585
00:28:31,400 --> 00:28:33,140
I told him before

586
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:34,300
to sort that out.

587
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:36,300
Don't end up like me,
alone all these years.

588
00:28:36,520 --> 00:28:37,100
No,

589
00:28:37,800 --> 00:28:39,340
it's not like that…

590
00:28:40,040 --> 00:28:42,740
He's just focused on work.

591
00:28:43,360 --> 00:28:44,700
I mean, I am too…

592
00:28:44,720 --> 00:28:45,260
I mean…

593
00:28:45,280 --> 00:28:46,180
I get it.

594
00:28:46,520 --> 00:28:47,580
Work matters.

595
00:28:48,520 --> 00:28:50,020
But life matters, too.

596
00:28:50,920 --> 00:28:51,820
I'll talk to him.

597
00:28:52,240 --> 00:28:54,700
He needs to guard the border

598
00:28:55,120 --> 00:28:57,020
and take care of his own life.

599
00:28:59,840 --> 00:29:01,020
Don't end up like me.

600
00:29:01,160 --> 00:29:03,420
My mother worried about me
her whole life.

601
00:29:03,760 --> 00:29:04,860
And in the end,

602
00:29:05,640 --> 00:29:07,500
she never got to enjoy family happiness.

603
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:10,700
What about Fei?

604
00:29:11,040 --> 00:29:13,300
Besides making you noodles,

605
00:29:13,400 --> 00:29:14,900
didn't things ever go further?

606
00:29:16,280 --> 00:29:18,860
Look at me now.
I'd just be holding her back.

607
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:22,420
If two people care about each other,
how is that holding someone back?

608
00:29:28,200 --> 00:29:28,860
Fei.

609
00:29:30,320 --> 00:29:32,060
You know my temper.

610
00:29:33,600 --> 00:29:34,940
And I'm a workaholic.

611
00:29:35,840 --> 00:29:38,180
When I'm working, nothing else matters.

612
00:29:38,800 --> 00:29:40,580
If you married me,

613
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:42,060
it'd basically be

614
00:29:42,240 --> 00:29:43,180
a marriage

615
00:29:43,200 --> 00:29:44,460
where you're alone anyway.

616
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:45,940
I can't be that selfish,

617
00:29:46,520 --> 00:29:48,180
always taking from you

618
00:29:48,520 --> 00:29:50,100
and giving nothing back.

619
00:29:55,840 --> 00:29:57,820
What if I don't care?

620
00:29:59,840 --> 00:30:03,260
What if I'm willing to give?

621
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:04,260
Fei.

622
00:30:05,640 --> 00:30:07,020
I know how good

623
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:09,380
you've been to me.

624
00:30:10,080 --> 00:30:11,260
I really do.

625
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:13,460
But

626
00:30:13,720 --> 00:30:15,300
I'm pushing 50.

627
00:30:15,840 --> 00:30:17,980
No house, no car, and no time.

628
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:19,740
And most of all,

629
00:30:22,680 --> 00:30:24,580
I don't even know
how to take care of you.

630
00:30:27,280 --> 00:30:27,980
You'd

631
00:30:28,160 --> 00:30:29,060
have it rough

632
00:30:29,440 --> 00:30:31,020
marrying someone like me.

633
00:30:33,280 --> 00:30:33,900
Let it go.

634
00:30:38,720 --> 00:30:39,580
Chen,

635
00:30:42,200 --> 00:30:43,860
didn't you just say

636
00:30:44,760 --> 00:30:47,300
life and work both matter?

637
00:30:51,040 --> 00:30:52,380
Why not try it?

638
00:30:52,480 --> 00:30:54,380
Take a step forward.

639
00:30:56,840 --> 00:30:57,580
No.

640
00:30:58,960 --> 00:30:59,700
I'm too old.

641
00:31:00,360 --> 00:31:02,620
My mind's all over the place lately.

642
00:31:02,920 --> 00:31:03,900
I can't think straight.

643
00:31:03,920 --> 00:31:05,460
Can't remember things.

644
00:31:07,600 --> 00:31:08,580
I'd just drag you down.

645
00:31:09,760 --> 00:31:10,860
Look at you.

646
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:13,740
You're at your prime

647
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:15,180
and you're beautiful.

648
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:17,780
Why

649
00:31:18,280 --> 00:31:20,540
spend your time on an old man like me?

650
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:22,260
Find someone else.

651
00:31:23,080 --> 00:31:24,380
Someone better than me.

652
00:31:25,440 --> 00:31:26,100
Be good.

653
00:32:13,400 --> 00:32:14,500
Hey, what's wrong?

654
00:32:14,720 --> 00:32:15,700
Nothing.

655
00:32:15,920 --> 00:32:18,540
Did Cong snap at you

656
00:32:18,920 --> 00:32:20,100
from work stress?

657
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:21,780
Tell me.

658
00:32:22,120 --> 00:32:23,300
I'll deal with him.

659
00:32:24,440 --> 00:32:25,500
You said it.

660
00:32:25,720 --> 00:32:26,300
I'll beat him up.

661
00:32:26,880 --> 00:32:27,540
Really?

662
00:32:28,080 --> 00:32:28,580
How?

663
00:32:28,600 --> 00:32:29,700
I… I'll…

664
00:32:29,720 --> 00:32:30,140
"Come here!

665
00:32:30,400 --> 00:32:31,580
Stick your butt out!"

666
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:32,500
I'll smack him right here.

667
00:32:35,080 --> 00:32:36,220
You've got a great trainee.

668
00:32:36,560 --> 00:32:37,780
He was well-behaved

669
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:38,660
back in training.

670
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:41,180
That's sour.

671
00:32:44,600 --> 00:32:45,140
Slow down.

672
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:47,340
She's alright.

673
00:32:48,400 --> 00:32:49,340
Just stubborn.

674
00:32:50,120 --> 00:32:50,780
Stubborn?

675
00:32:51,800 --> 00:32:52,780
That's good,

676
00:32:52,880 --> 00:32:53,300
right?

677
00:32:53,320 --> 00:32:54,740
You three are all stubborn.

678
00:32:55,400 --> 00:32:55,900
Oh,

679
00:32:55,960 --> 00:32:56,460
right.

680
00:32:57,360 --> 00:33:00,220
My photography exhibition
is pretty much ready.

681
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:03,340
When it opens, bring her along.

682
00:33:03,360 --> 00:33:04,380
Come check it out.

683
00:33:04,520 --> 00:33:04,980
Okay?

684
00:33:05,480 --> 00:33:06,260
Alright, got it.

685
00:33:13,320 --> 00:33:13,820
Cong,

686
00:33:14,320 --> 00:33:15,420
when's your mom's flight?

687
00:33:15,720 --> 00:33:16,700
I can have someone

688
00:33:16,720 --> 00:33:18,260
pick her up at the airport.

689
00:33:18,840 --> 00:33:19,700
It's fine.

690
00:33:20,080 --> 00:33:20,820
I checked.

691
00:33:20,840 --> 00:33:21,740
I'm off that day.

692
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:22,580
Alright.

693
00:33:22,600 --> 00:33:23,140
I'll drop it.

694
00:33:23,160 --> 00:33:23,580
Okay.

695
00:33:23,720 --> 00:33:25,180
Drive safe on your way back.

696
00:33:25,520 --> 00:33:25,940
Got it.

697
00:33:25,960 --> 00:33:26,660
Call me if anything comes up.

698
00:33:26,680 --> 00:33:27,100
Okay.

699
00:33:35,520 --> 00:33:36,540
Drive safe.

700
00:33:40,320 --> 00:33:40,700
Let's go.

701
00:33:40,800 --> 00:33:41,300
Get in.

702
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:44,100
It's fine. Not on your way.

703
00:33:44,280 --> 00:33:45,380
I'll grab a cab.

704
00:33:46,080 --> 00:33:46,540
Oh, right.

705
00:33:47,440 --> 00:33:49,580
Who exactly is Fei?

706
00:33:50,520 --> 00:33:52,220
What did my mentor tell you about her?

707
00:33:52,440 --> 00:33:53,540
I can't tell you that.

708
00:33:53,680 --> 00:33:55,740
Not unless you tell me who she is first.

709
00:33:56,080 --> 00:33:56,540
Fine.

710
00:33:57,280 --> 00:33:58,220
Tomorrow at noon.

711
00:33:58,360 --> 00:33:59,420
I'll text you the address.

712
00:33:59,640 --> 00:34:01,340
Get in. I'll take you back.

713
00:34:16,600 --> 00:34:23,120
[Seafood Night Stall]

714
00:34:23,120 --> 00:34:25,000
[2015
Eight Years Ago]

715
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:25,610
Mentor,

716
00:34:25,610 --> 00:34:26,710
[2015
Eight Years Ago]

717
00:34:26,710 --> 00:34:29,420
this is the sea Michelin
you were talking about?

718
00:34:30,710 --> 00:34:30,980
Hold this.

719
00:34:31,630 --> 00:34:32,300
Listen,

720
00:34:32,600 --> 00:34:33,980
you can joke like that with me,

721
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:36,740
[Seafood Night Stall]
but don't say it in front of the owner.

722
00:34:36,920 --> 00:34:37,860
[Seafood Night Stall]
You're cold?

723
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:38,980
[Seafood Night Stall]
Mind your own business.

724
00:34:39,320 --> 00:34:40,020
[Seafood Night Stall]
Well, if she beats you up,

725
00:34:40,080 --> 00:34:40,860
[Seafood Night Stall]
I'm staying out of it.

726
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:44,580
Don't be fooled

727
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:46,170
by the size of the place.

728
00:34:47,160 --> 00:34:48,580
The food's incredible.

729
00:34:49,040 --> 00:34:49,860
Watch your head.

730
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:58,540
Slow down, don't rock it.

731
00:34:58,600 --> 00:35:00,100
You work in Customs,
and you're scared of the sea?

732
00:35:00,200 --> 00:35:00,580
What's that

733
00:35:00,640 --> 00:35:02,260
got to do with Customs?

734
00:35:02,600 --> 00:35:03,180
Stop rocking.

735
00:35:03,480 --> 00:35:04,020
Fei!

736
00:35:05,440 --> 00:35:06,100
Mr. Chen's here.

737
00:35:06,960 --> 00:35:07,460
Fei!

738
00:35:10,960 --> 00:35:11,500
Fei!

739
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:14,180
Fei!

740
00:35:14,600 --> 00:35:15,580
Two oil-splashed noodles.

741
00:35:15,640 --> 00:35:15,820
Quick.

742
00:35:16,160 --> 00:35:16,700
I need food.

743
00:35:17,040 --> 00:35:17,660
Uh…

744
00:35:18,280 --> 00:35:18,980
low blood sugar.

745
00:35:20,400 --> 00:35:22,460
All dressed up like this,
what's the occasion?

746
00:35:23,720 --> 00:35:24,340
Handsome, right?

747
00:35:24,600 --> 00:35:26,020
Spent the whole day 'playing dad'.

748
00:35:28,800 --> 00:35:29,900
Instant fatherhood?

749
00:35:31,160 --> 00:35:32,780
Late-life surprise, huh?

750
00:35:34,080 --> 00:35:34,660
No, no.

751
00:35:35,120 --> 00:35:36,180
Let me introduce you.

752
00:35:36,760 --> 00:35:38,300
This is my trainee, Guo Cong.

753
00:35:38,880 --> 00:35:39,340
Say hello.

754
00:35:42,480 --> 00:35:43,140
Hello, Madam.

755
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:45,140
Fei.

756
00:35:45,320 --> 00:35:46,700
Just call me Fei.

757
00:35:47,600 --> 00:35:48,460
Have a seat.

758
00:35:48,520 --> 00:35:49,740
I'll get your noodles.

759
00:35:50,080 --> 00:35:50,860
Thanks, Fei.

760
00:35:55,600 --> 00:35:56,060
What's wrong?

761
00:35:56,160 --> 00:35:56,980
What do you mean, "what's wrong"?
Sit down.

762
00:35:57,160 --> 00:35:58,580
I just felt like she is kind of…

763
00:35:58,640 --> 00:35:59,340
Alright. Shut up.

764
00:36:00,160 --> 00:36:00,700
Mentor,

765
00:36:01,200 --> 00:36:02,020
is Fei…?

766
00:36:02,240 --> 00:36:02,700
Mr. Chen,

767
00:36:02,760 --> 00:36:03,260
I'll get you another set.

768
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:03,620
Okay.

769
00:36:03,680 --> 00:36:05,140
Thank you.

770
00:36:07,360 --> 00:36:08,260
I'm telling you,

771
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:11,540
their noodles are something else.

772
00:36:12,160 --> 00:36:13,580
Every trade

773
00:36:13,640 --> 00:36:14,540
has its masters.

774
00:36:14,800 --> 00:36:16,500
If you put your heart into it,

775
00:36:16,560 --> 00:36:18,140
you can do what others can't.

776
00:36:18,960 --> 00:36:19,500
Mentor,

777
00:36:19,560 --> 00:36:21,460
we're off work. Can you give it a rest?

778
00:36:22,040 --> 00:36:23,460
Lessons don't clock out.

779
00:36:24,960 --> 00:36:26,300
But I've already taught you

780
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:27,260
everything I can teach you.

781
00:36:27,840 --> 00:36:29,900
From today on,
you're done with the basics.

782
00:36:30,880 --> 00:36:32,060
That fast?

783
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:33,540
We've barely

784
00:36:33,600 --> 00:36:34,740
learned anything.

785
00:36:34,920 --> 00:36:36,700
What I taught you
was how to approach a problem.

786
00:36:36,760 --> 00:36:37,660
But solving it…

787
00:36:37,720 --> 00:36:39,940
That's on you. You learn in the field

788
00:36:40,080 --> 00:36:41,540
by reflecting and improving.

789
00:36:41,760 --> 00:36:42,540
You've got

790
00:36:42,960 --> 00:36:44,620
the makings
of a great Passenger Inspection officer.

791
00:36:44,800 --> 00:36:46,620
But talent alone won't get you there.

792
00:36:47,360 --> 00:36:48,180
No shortcuts.

793
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:50,740
It all comes down to practice.

794
00:36:50,800 --> 00:36:51,300
Got it?

795
00:36:55,240 --> 00:36:55,860
Got it, Mentor.

796
00:36:56,680 --> 00:36:57,300
Don't worry.

797
00:36:57,360 --> 00:36:58,100
I won't fail you.

798
00:37:00,040 --> 00:37:00,980
Sit down and eat.

799
00:37:01,040 --> 00:37:01,380
Okay.

800
00:37:03,280 --> 00:37:04,260
Your trainee

801
00:37:04,560 --> 00:37:05,620
likes standing around.

802
00:37:06,080 --> 00:37:07,220
Let him. Looks solid that way.

803
00:37:10,440 --> 00:37:11,620
Not hand-pulled noodles?

804
00:37:12,280 --> 00:37:13,340
You'll have to make do.

805
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:14,340
Out of noodles today.

806
00:37:15,040 --> 00:37:15,380
Alright.

807
00:37:18,680 --> 00:37:19,180
Mentor,

808
00:37:19,440 --> 00:37:20,740
we missed the signature dish.

809
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:22,020
This is good, too.

810
00:37:22,240 --> 00:37:22,580
Eat.

811
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:26,780
Here.

812
00:37:27,120 --> 00:37:27,980
Extra dishes.

813
00:37:28,040 --> 00:37:28,780
That's plenty.

814
00:37:28,960 --> 00:37:29,740
Thanks, Fei.

815
00:37:30,360 --> 00:37:31,140
It's really good.

816
00:37:34,520 --> 00:37:34,900
Mentor,

817
00:37:35,040 --> 00:37:36,500
you and Fei, huh?

818
00:37:37,280 --> 00:37:37,660
Right?

819
00:37:38,360 --> 00:37:38,860
Eat.

820
00:37:43,440 --> 00:37:44,740
You're grinning ear to ear.

821
00:37:49,560 --> 00:37:54,640
[Seafood Night Stall]

822
00:38:16,480 --> 00:38:19,200
[Seafood Night Stall]

823
00:38:21,240 --> 00:38:21,860
Mentor.

824
00:38:33,560 --> 00:38:36,460
You and Mr. Chen really had good taste.

825
00:38:36,760 --> 00:38:38,260
This place is beautiful.

826
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:41,100
Keep it down.

827
00:38:41,200 --> 00:38:42,300
There are other guests.

828
00:38:44,040 --> 00:38:45,460
This was my mentor's spot.

829
00:38:46,400 --> 00:38:48,580
First time he brought me out,
it was here.

830
00:38:49,320 --> 00:38:52,300
I still remember
where you first took me.

831
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:53,020
Wasn't it

832
00:38:53,080 --> 00:38:54,500
that Hangzhou snack place?

833
00:38:54,840 --> 00:38:56,660
Bit of a difference, don't you think?

834
00:38:57,200 --> 00:38:57,980
That one doesn't count.

835
00:39:04,440 --> 00:39:05,060
Careful.

836
00:39:05,240 --> 00:39:05,860
Hold on to something.

837
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:09,540
Fei!

838
00:39:11,200 --> 00:39:11,740
Watch your step.

839
00:39:12,400 --> 00:39:12,860
Slow down.

840
00:39:13,240 --> 00:39:14,260
Fei!

841
00:39:14,560 --> 00:39:15,580
Coming.

842
00:39:22,640 --> 00:39:23,220
Cong,

843
00:39:23,280 --> 00:39:23,860
you're here.

844
00:39:24,800 --> 00:39:25,420
And this is…?

845
00:39:25,480 --> 00:39:25,980
Hello, Fei.

846
00:39:26,320 --> 00:39:27,140
I'm Zhang Yu.

847
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,500
Guo Cong's trainee.

848
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:30,420
Nice to meet you.

849
00:39:30,640 --> 00:39:32,220
This place is gorgeous.

850
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:33,180
Sea on all sides.

851
00:39:33,560 --> 00:39:35,180
It's like a full-on seaside restaurant.

852
00:39:35,440 --> 00:39:36,100
Cong,

853
00:39:36,360 --> 00:39:38,140
you and your mentor
have been here so many times

854
00:39:38,160 --> 00:39:39,980
and never said a word about the view.

855
00:39:40,400 --> 00:39:41,140
Zhang,

856
00:39:41,240 --> 00:39:42,380
just for that,

857
00:39:42,520 --> 00:39:44,300
I'm putting in a proper spread for you.

858
00:39:44,640 --> 00:39:45,860
Come on, go sit inside.

859
00:39:45,880 --> 00:39:46,180
Okay.

860
00:39:46,200 --> 00:39:47,300
I'll have someone clean this up.

861
00:39:47,320 --> 00:39:48,020
Thanks, Fei.

862
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:50,020
Xiao Deng,

863
00:39:50,360 --> 00:39:52,020
- come clear this. - Got it.

864
00:40:03,120 --> 00:40:03,740
A seagull.

865
00:40:05,280 --> 00:40:06,100
Egret.

866
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:12,980
This place still feels nice.

867
00:40:15,640 --> 00:40:16,420
Yeah.

868
00:40:18,160 --> 00:40:19,660
This is where I became a trainee.

869
00:40:23,360 --> 00:40:24,100
So…

870
00:40:24,720 --> 00:40:27,980
I guess this is where
I formally become a trainee, too.

871
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:30,020
I never said that.

872
00:40:30,040 --> 00:40:30,780
Mentor Guo Cong.

873
00:40:32,320 --> 00:40:34,060
I have a humble request.

874
00:40:36,440 --> 00:40:36,940
Go ahead.

875
00:40:38,360 --> 00:40:40,500
Can I have my resignation letter back?

876
00:40:40,520 --> 00:40:41,420
No.

877
00:40:41,720 --> 00:40:42,620
Why not?

878
00:40:42,640 --> 00:40:44,180
You quit too much.

879
00:40:44,200 --> 00:40:45,020
I'll keep it.

880
00:40:45,040 --> 00:40:46,060
You'll need it again.

881
00:40:46,960 --> 00:40:48,540
Fair enough.

882
00:40:49,760 --> 00:40:50,740
You hang on to it then.

883
00:40:51,400 --> 00:40:53,620
Keeps me on my toes.

884
00:40:56,560 --> 00:40:57,980
I've messed up before, too.

885
00:40:58,280 --> 00:40:59,060
No way.

886
00:40:59,080 --> 00:40:59,740
Calm down.

887
00:40:59,760 --> 00:41:01,020
You've had your moments of doubt, too?

888
00:41:01,040 --> 00:41:02,260
Only you're allowed

889
00:41:02,280 --> 00:41:03,460
to be a handful? I'm not?

890
00:41:03,480 --> 00:41:04,580
Wait, I remember.

891
00:41:05,680 --> 00:41:06,820
That time…

892
00:41:07,280 --> 00:41:08,460
"You don't need me here?"

893
00:41:08,560 --> 00:41:10,180
Mr. Shen really laid into you.

894
00:41:10,800 --> 00:41:11,380
What was it…

895
00:41:12,120 --> 00:41:12,780
"Reckless.

896
00:41:13,720 --> 00:41:14,300
Undisciplined."

897
00:41:14,320 --> 00:41:15,340
He was exaggerating.

898
00:41:15,840 --> 00:41:17,940
Then give me
the non-exaggerated version.

899
00:41:18,600 --> 00:41:20,260
Call it a cautionary tale.

900
00:41:20,280 --> 00:41:21,340
Help me learn from it.

901
00:41:21,560 --> 00:41:23,020
Next time we see Mr. Chen,

902
00:41:23,040 --> 00:41:24,300
I can even help remind him.

903
00:41:25,520 --> 00:41:26,020
Sound good?

904
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:42,800
[2015
Eight Years Ago]

905
00:41:42,800 --> 00:41:44,740
[Binhai Customs Training Center]
Welcome to initial training.

906
00:41:45,160 --> 00:41:46,180
I'm Chen Sanhe,

907
00:41:46,640 --> 00:41:47,820
your class instructor.

908
00:41:48,200 --> 00:41:49,300
You can also call me Mr. Chen.

909
00:41:49,880 --> 00:41:51,500
This is Shen Xuejun,

910
00:41:51,720 --> 00:41:53,060
your deputy instructor.

911
00:41:57,080 --> 00:41:58,260
Did I tell you to clap?

912
00:42:00,640 --> 00:42:01,940
Listen carefully.

913
00:42:03,440 --> 00:42:04,420
Move when ordered.

914
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:06,020
Stop when told.

915
00:42:06,880 --> 00:42:08,140
That is discipline.

916
00:42:08,600 --> 00:42:09,300
Understood?

917
00:42:09,440 --> 00:42:10,460
Understood!

918
00:42:12,160 --> 00:42:12,900
All units.

919
00:42:14,520 --> 00:42:15,300
Stand at attention.

920
00:42:16,200 --> 00:42:16,740
Head up.

921
00:42:17,200 --> 00:42:17,820
Chest out.

922
00:42:17,960 --> 00:42:18,900
Eyes forward.

923
00:42:19,600 --> 00:42:21,020
This is the most basic stance.

924
00:42:21,960 --> 00:42:23,500
When you step into Customs,

925
00:42:23,640 --> 00:42:25,820
I expect every one of you

926
00:42:26,240 --> 00:42:28,220
to carry yourselves
like Customs officers,

927
00:42:28,400 --> 00:42:29,900
in both bearing and spirit.

928
00:42:30,560 --> 00:42:31,500
Stand properly.

929
00:42:31,800 --> 00:42:32,620
Sit properly.

930
00:42:33,560 --> 00:42:34,340
Know why?

931
00:42:35,920 --> 00:42:37,860
Because one day, you'll be standing

932
00:42:38,160 --> 00:42:39,900
on the front line of the border.

933
00:42:40,160 --> 00:42:41,900
You represent the image of the country.

934
00:42:42,480 --> 00:42:44,020
When facing returning citizens

935
00:42:44,240 --> 00:42:45,220
and international visitors,

936
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:46,940
you must be composed

937
00:42:47,040 --> 00:42:47,940
and approachable.

938
00:42:48,240 --> 00:42:49,980
When facing smugglers,

939
00:42:50,960 --> 00:42:52,220
you must be intimidating,

940
00:42:52,640 --> 00:42:53,980
commanding, and unshakable.

941
00:42:54,240 --> 00:42:54,820
Understood?

942
00:42:55,080 --> 00:42:55,900
Understood!

943
00:42:56,040 --> 00:42:56,660
I can't hear you.

944
00:42:56,760 --> 00:42:57,780
Understood!

945
00:43:30,800 --> 00:43:37,360
♪There's a place of simple,
everyday warmth♪

946
00:43:38,280 --> 00:43:45,000
♪There's a place of simple,
everyday warmth♪

947
00:43:45,920 --> 00:43:52,440
♪A humble table still warm with love♪

948
00:43:52,680 --> 00:43:56,320
♪After you've tasted every high and low♪

949
00:43:56,600 --> 00:44:00,240
♪Come home, I'll keep you warm♪

950
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:07,680
♪Where the days begin and end♪

951
00:44:08,400 --> 00:44:15,320
♪A light still on for the ones
who've lost their way♪

952
00:44:16,120 --> 00:44:22,680
♪An embrace waiting just for you♪

953
00:44:22,960 --> 00:44:26,680
♪Through every passing season♪

954
00:44:26,800 --> 00:44:30,480
♪Even if you return with nothing at all♪

955
00:44:31,120 --> 00:44:34,600
♪Turn around and look♪

956
00:44:34,800 --> 00:44:38,600
♪That door's still open♪

957
00:44:38,800 --> 00:44:42,440
♪A light still burning♪

958
00:44:42,520 --> 00:44:46,240
♪Waiting there for you♪

959
00:44:46,400 --> 00:44:49,920
♪Turn around and look♪

960
00:44:50,160 --> 00:44:53,960
♪Someone's still waiting♪

961
00:44:54,160 --> 00:44:57,760
♪Watching the dusk settle in♪

962
00:44:57,840 --> 00:45:01,560
♪Waiting for the break of dawn♪

963
00:45:03,320 --> 00:45:06,960
♪It's always there♪
